<h1>Service Desk</h1>
<p>The menu in the <em>Administration - Service Desk</em> section is used to administer the <a href="../../../alvao-service-desk">ALVAO Service Desk</a> system.</p>
<p>Features:</p>
<ul>
  <li><a href="service-desk/service">Services</a> - service management.b</li>
  <li><a href="service-desk/sla">SLA</a> - manage SLA.</li>
  <li><a href="service-desk/process">Processes</a> - management of processes, i.e. workflow requests.</li>
  <li><a href="service-desk/operating-hours">Operating Hours</a> - managing service operating hours.</li>
  <li><a href="service-desk/approval-scheme">Approval schemes</a> - management of approval schemes used to automate approval workflows.</li>
  <li><a href="service-desk/roles-messages">Rules for incoming messages</a> - set up rules to automatically process incoming email messages.</li>
  <li><a href="service-desk/settings">Settings</a> - additional settings for the ALVAO Service Desk system.</li>
</ul>

